@startuml
title GitOps Release Flow
actor Engineer
participant Git as "Git Repository"
participant CI as "CI Pipeline"
participant CD as "CD/Reconciler"
participant OCI as "OCI Runtime"

Engineer -> Git: commit change
Git -> CI: trigger validation
CI -> CI: test, scan, package
CI -> CD: approve promotion
CD -> OCI: apply desired state
OCI --> CD: deployment status
CD --> Git: record release metadata
@enduml
